Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:26.83,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur20}都归咎于温柔的你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.84,0:24:33.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur20}你的眉头紧锁
